summary: New Acoustic Guitar music for the game
descriptionHtml:
This is my attempt to create a recognisable theme for the Tamriel world on my Acoustic guitar. I am praying someone out there can MOD this MP3 into the game for me a I am useless in this area.. 
 I was thinking the first part of the music for the INTRO or the whole piece as one of the Bards list at one of the local inn\'s. :oD  .....anyone :o)  

CHECK IT OUT AT
